
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-ecrit-trustworthy-location-14.txt'>
    <title>"Trustworthy Location", Hannes Tschofenig, Henning Schulzrinne, Bernard Aboba</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-ecrit-trustworthy-location-14.txt</link>
    <description>The trustworthiness of location information is critically important for some location-based applications, such as emergency calling or roadside assistance.  This document describes threats relating to conveyance of location in an emergency call, and describes techniques that improve the reliability and security of location information conveyed in a IP- based emergency service call.  It also provides guidelines for assessing the trustworthiness of location information.</description>
    <dc:date>2014-07-28T07:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
